channel.description:

"Error Game Js5connect", I CANNOT AND NEITHER CAN ANYONE WHO HAS HELPED FIGURE THIS OUT! So if someone a lot smarter than I or anyone I have been working with care to help and and possibly take a look, please.. Be my guest.
